casebody.data:
Jeromy Michael RUCKDASCHEL, Petitioner,
v.
The FOURTH JUDICIAL DISTRICT COURT of the State of Nevada, IN AND FOR the COUNTY OF ELKO; and the Honorable Nancy L. Porter, District Judge, Respondents,
and
the State of Nevada, Real Party in Interest. No. 79003 Supreme Court of Nevada. FILED JULY 05, 2019

Elko County Public Defender

Attorney General/Carson City

Elko County District Attorney

ORDER DISMISSING PETITION

This is a petition for a writ of mandamus. Fourth Judicial District Court, Elko County; Judge.

Petitioner has filed a notice of withdrawal of the petition. Cause appearing, the court

ORDERS this petition DISMISSED.
